jQuery.cyclify()

This is a jQuery plugin that lets the user cycle through a bunch of divs, one at a time.

Requires these jQuery and these CSS classes to work:

wrapper-class *can be any class*
    cycle-controls
        cycle-prev
        cycle-next
        cycle-begin
        cycle-end
    cycle-cycles
        div
        div
        div
        ...

USAGE:
  // all options are optional
  $('.wrapper-class').cyclify({
    loop       : true,
    transition : 'linear',
    delay      : 100,
    success : function(current_div) {
      alert('the current div is ' + $(current_div));
    }
  });
